              "quote": "The application of the ontology is an adequate approach for automating the capture of an EA model evolution, which leverages the tracking of change in the current EA model and provides views to aid the impact analysis of planning changes in enterprise APIs, and, finally, for monitoring the effects of the architectural change's implementation, contributing to an agile EA management.",
              "section": "Conclusion and Future Work"
