            {
              "quote": "This work evolves the ontology to follow the FAIR principles (Findability, Accessibility, Interoperability, and Reusability) to facilitate its publication in the FAIR multi-domain catalog for Ontology-Driven Conceptual Modeling 3 and promote its reuse and extension to other cases.",
              "section": "5.2 Ontology Requirements"
